<P>

<s docid="LA052289-0053" num="43"> DEPORTATION; ESPIONAGE -- USSR; ESPIONAGE -- ENGLAND; ENGLAND -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; ENGLANG -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; USSR -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS</s>
</P>
