<s docid="FBIS4-36856" num="13"> BFN [Text] Responding to a question regarding a news report published in a local English daily alleging the expulsion of two Pakistani diplomats from Germany, a Foreign Office spokesman said in Islamabad today that the report by German television was factually incorrect.</s>

<s docid="FBIS4-36856" num="14"> No Pakistani diplomat has been expelled from Germany as asserted in the report.</s>

<s docid="FBIS4-36856" num="15"> The spokesman said Pakistan is procuring a number of sophisticated items of [as heard] equipment from various sources.</s>

